    {
      "chinese": "泰雅祖先有三兄弟從發源地「Pinsbkan」往北方遷徙，翻越梨山，下到碧綠溪，行經松茂部落，前往南湖溪與大甲溪與七加灣溪所匯聚的地方，就是現今「清泉橋」的位置。沿著溪河上游抵達勝光聚落，前進到勝光「Hlusan」鞍部，最後抵達思源埡口。",
      "ab": "maki qa tyugan mcwahi mlikuy kahul kya Pinsbkan, wayan mshyi mkura kya te kraya, mtayil kya qalang Slamaw, mbiyaq kya gong Tyuku mkura qalang Tabuk, mbiyaq gong Topuk ki llyung Tamali wan msqun gong Sqyawan, maki kya hbun Sburuq, mkura kya llyung kraya ga baq nta kya quri Hlusan, pucing lga mqasux kya quri Sqabu la.",
